K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:323b-1: a'arya pra t'i tya sa mutp'a da n'a ma mah'a ya na s'u tra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:323b-3: 'phags pa rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:323b-7: bcom ldan 'das sum cu rtsa gsum lha'i gnas na aar mo ni ga lta bu'i rdo leb la tshe dang ldan pa rta thul la sogs pa nyan thos chen po rnams dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324a-0: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyan ras gzigs dbang phyug stan las langs te bla gos phrag pa gcig tu gzar nas pus mo g-yas pa'i lha nga ri rab kyi rtse mo la btsugs te @324a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324a-1: bcom ldan 'das ga la ba de logs su thal mo sbyar ba btud nas bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324a-3: lha 'di dag ni; mchod rten bgyid par 'tshal ba sha stag ste /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324a-10: bram zer bcas pa'i skye rgyu las dge slong dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324a-13: dge bsnyen ma dag bsod nams shin tu mang du 'phel bar 'gyur ba de lta de ltar bcom ldan 'das kyis de dag la chos bstan du gsol /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324a-15: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba'i tshigs su bcad pa bka' stsal pa /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324a-17: ti sh'anytsa yo ni ro dha ae bam b'a d'i ma h'a shr'a ma na:/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324a-18: chos gang rgyus byung de dag gi /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324a-20: de bzhin gshegs pas bka' stsal te //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324b-0: sus rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba mthong ba des de bzhin @324b gshegs pa mthong ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324b-3: rigs kyi bu mo dad pa can gang la la zhig gis mi gnas pa'i sa phyogs su mchod rten ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324b-8: ba ku la'i me tog tsam zhig byas la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324b-9: rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba chos kyi dbyings kyi tshigs su bcad pa nan gdu bzhung na; des tshangs pa'i bsod nams bskyed par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324b-10: 'di nas shi 'phos shing 'chi ba'i dus byas nas tshangs pa'i 'jig rten du skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-044:324b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas nyan thos de dag dang /
